{"tid":302791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雜種訪港】匿名境外來電轟炸 斷金紫荊佔領者通訊","createTime":"2017-06-29T15:54:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T23:00:50.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"49ffeb7fa35bbc6d065a94f704a5a145125a99f2","tid":302791,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T15:54:51.000Z","msg":"國家主席習近平本月29日至7月1日將訪港，灣仔金紫荊廣場繼兩日前清晨遭黑布包圍後，逾20名自決派下午5時許再次佔領金紫荊雕像，其中爬上雕像的社民連主席吳文遠表示，一眾留守雕像的示威者，晚上不約而同遭匿名來電密集式滋擾。<br />\n<br />\n吳文遠指，現場暫時共有7名示威者遭來電滋擾，接聽後對方自動播放錄音：「呢個係海外嘅來電&hellip;&hellip;」、「（錄音）句說話都未講完，下一個call又入嚟」，情況一直持續，直至示威者熄機。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，匿名來電幾乎每秒打入一次，導致示威者無法與外界通訊，「搞到個電話用都用唔到」。同樣佔領雕像的眾志黃之鋒、羅冠聰，以及社民連梁國雄、黃浩銘等人一同遭殃。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170628/56888789\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170628%2F56888789&d=Jkk4H3fGldFjjD1F5YmC2Izu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=3aa6b41f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170628%2F56888789&h=18316ba3\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170628/56888789</a><br />\n<br />\n你話啲電話騙案同共產黨有冇關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b367655c9b1c18a7b78ade977d9fa14b16d20b2","tid":302791,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T22:59:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"06a3f7ee1a18812c5919596fdc143e5fa09e3ff2","tid":302791,"uid":609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:00:50.000Z","msg":"唔係話用iphone好安全架咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}